articles.title: Teenage girl killed in shark attack in Australia - BBC.com
articles.description: The 17-year-old was attacked around 100m from shore of Woormin Beach, Australian media reports.
articles.content:
A teenage girl has died after being attacked by a shark in Queensland, Australia.
